'''三星Galaxy S21'''（{{lang-en|Samsung Galaxy S21}}）是一款由[[三星電子|三星電子]]設計、生產、銷售和製造的智能手機系列產品<ref>{{Cite web|title=Should you buy the Galaxy S21 series or the Galaxy S20 series?|url=https://www.xda-developers.com/samsung-galaxy-s21-vs-s20-series/|accessdate=2021-01-25|author=|date=2021-01-23|format=|publisher=''xda-developers''|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508123412/https://www.xda-developers.com/samsung-galaxy-s21-vs-s20-series/}}</ref>，屬該公司[[三星Galaxy_S系列|Galaxy S系列]]的一部份<ref>{{Cite web|title=SAMSUNG GALAXY S21, S21 PLUS, AND S21 ULTRA FIRST LOOK: POLISHED DESIGN (AND PRICES)|url=https://www.theverge.com/22227772/samsung-galaxy-s21-plus-ultra-price-specs-release-date-unpacked|accessdate=2021-01-14|last=Gartenberg|first=Chaim|date=2021-01-14|format=|publisher=''The Verge''|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114150216/https://www.theverge.com/22227772/samsung-galaxy-s21-plus-ultra-price-specs-release-date-unpacked|archivedate=2021-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該系列是[[三星Galaxy_S20|Galaxy S20系列]]的繼任者，前三款於2021年1月14日三星Galaxy Unpacked活動中亮相，FE於2022年1月3日CES 2022活動中亮相。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Galaxy UNPACKED 2021|url=https://www.samsung.com/global/galaxy/events/unpacked/|accessdate=2021-01-14|author=|date=|format=|publisher=''The Official Samsung Galaxy Site''|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113205704/https://www.samsung.com/global/galaxy/events/unpacked/|archivedate=2021-01-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==歷史==
網絡上有關該系列硬件配備的傳言早於2020年4至5月間出現，當時有傳言指2021年度的三星旗艦手機（即後來的Galaxy S21系列）將會配備1.5億像素的主鏡頭，亦有網民指出廠方正考慮在該產品中引入屏下鏡頭（under-screen camera）技術。<ref>{{Cite web|title=三星Galaxy S21傳搭1.5億畫素相機 5攝主鏡頭太威猛|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200612000018-260412?chdtv|accessdate=2021-01-28|author=黃慧雯|date=2020-06-12|format=|publisher=中時新聞網|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202092730/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200612000018-260412?chdtv}}</ref>

